name: My Dog Stepped On A Bee...

metadata.name: My Dog Stepped On A Bee #1
metadata.description: My Dog Stepped On A Bee! Find your favorite NFT and hopefully it will put a smile on your face. It’s for fun, it’s for free. Because not all crypto projects should be about finding the way to the metaverse, or the next super community development in the crypto space (mumble, mumble ;) ). We build memes and laugh while making them, we only hope it does the same to you... You will find here crypto and funny quotes of life. Not financial advice...
